20070254.text: The search gangs here... I thought they were strong, but they're filthy and dirty! \nThere, <textColor=[255:204:102:255]><myHero.name/></>.

20070255.text: I know the special training method that comes down to <textColor=[78:148:215:255]>Geumgyeongcheolmun</>...\nThis is <textColor=[78:148:215:255]>Pungbaekmun<

20070256.text: I can't tell you here, I'll see you in <textColor=[110:216:175:255]>Ashen Sky Forest</>. \nThen see you later!

20070257.text: You've been waiting a long time! There was nothing to be so nervous about...\nThe training method is simple. It's about killing the <textColor=[215:94:94:255]>Monsters</> here.

20070258.text: However, this is not a simple <textColor=[215:94:94:255]>extermination of monsters</>.\n In this training method, order and intensity are important, and the optimal training amount is <textColor=[255:204:102:

20070259.text: First, try to get rid of <textColor=[215:94:94:255]>Dick</>.

20070260.text: How do you feel? Doesn't your body feel full of energy? \n If you keep doing this, you have a perfect feeling that you will become a climactic master! Ozzie?! Isn't it?!

20070261.text: Now, if you do this practice every day, you will definitely become stronger!

20070262.text: Be sure to inform the guys at the Joint Post about the effectiveness of this training method. \nEveryone looks up to this body and she can see me again... No, no!
